videos.description: Kyrie Irving penetrates into the paint and tosses a lob to DeAndre Jordan for a big one-handed finish for the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie lobs to DJ for easy slam) 2021/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie lobs to DJ for easy slam

videos.description: Kyrie Irving connects with DeAndre Jordan again on a lob, but this time Jordan throws down a sweet reverse dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (DJ throws down sweet reverse alley-oop jam) 2021/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: DJ throws down sweet reverse alley-oop jam

videos.description: Danny Green pokes the ball free for a steal then races down the court to throw down a one-handed dunk for the Sixers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Green gets the steal and fast-break bucket) 2021/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green gets the steal and fast-break bucket

videos.description: Ben Simmons throws a long-range pass to Tobias Harris who goes up to throw down a fast-break dunk for the Sixers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons finds Harris for a fast-break dunk) 2021/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons finds Harris for a fast-break dunk

videos.description: Joel Embiid uses a shot fake to shed his defender, then hurries to the basket to flush a two-handed dunk for the Sixers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid fakes defender for big finish at the rim) 2021/04/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid fakes defender for big finish at the rim

videos.description: Joel Embiid leads the way for 76ers with 39 points and 13 rebounds as they take down Kyrie Irving and the Nets 123-117.
